  "keyFeatures": [
    "Ultra-fast stabilizer circuit simulation using vectorized AVX instructions",
    "Reference frame sampling for bulk shot generation at kilohertz rates",
    "Automatic detector error model generation from noisy circuits",
    "Rich Python API with Circuit, Tableau, PauliString, and TableauSimulator classes",
    "Command-line interface for scripting and pipeline integration",
    "Sinter subproject for parallel Monte Carlo QEC sampling",
    "Support for 100+ Clifford gates, noise channels, and measurement operations",
    "Crumble interactive circuit editor for visualization"
  ],
